name: Substrate Aluminium Vol.1
description:
All New 'Substrate Aluminium' Series.

LIMITED EDITION Ultrascope/Paradox Signed 12" Acetate. 

ONLY 10 Unique Cuts Available.

Side A : Ultrascope - Paradox III (SA Master MIx) 
Side B : Ultrascope - Paradox IV (SA Master MIx) 

Also includes 24-bit Acetate Master Recordings on Data CD
+'Time Paradox' album access code

Details:

An aluminium platter covered in cellulose nitrate then cut with a ruby - the result is a greater audio quality than pressed vinyl. An acetate is suitable for hundreds of plays with a tonal change after around 50. A first play 24-bit recording is supplied with each cut for listening and archival.

Both tracks have been re-mixed, mastered and then cut to the acetate. 

The tracks are alternate timeline mixes of 'Ultrascope' and 'Over World' 

---------------
SPECIAL ORDER ITEM - Ships within 14 Working Days

Please Note due to Xmas post orders from outside the UK will ship early January.
--------------

Postage info: All orders are shipped tracked 

More about SA Series -  http://wp.me/pyzET-1qs
